Features
Decentralized Betting: Fully trustless and transparent system using blockchain smart contracts.
Custom Bet Conditions: Users can define and agree on custom bet conditions.
Secure Fund Handling: Funds are securely locked in smart contracts until the bet is resolved.
Automated Payouts: Smart contracts handle winner verification and release funds automatically.
Blockchain Integration: Uses Ethereum or compatible blockchain networks for secure transactions.
Scalable and Extendable: Built to support future features like Oracle integration for dynamic bets.
